00:58:13,308 --> 00:58:15,109
I'll go this way.

552
00:59:04,927 --> 00:59:07,195
[woman crying]

553
00:59:09,431 --> 00:59:11,699
You have reached
the office of Alex Scott,

554
00:59:11,733 --> 00:59:14,135
Senior Financial Analyst
at Green Brothers Capital.

555
00:59:14,169 --> 00:59:16,404
Leave a message
at the tone or press pound

556
00:59:16,438 --> 00:59:18,472
