557
00:59:18,507 --> 00:59:20,341
[machine beeps]

558
00:59:20,375 --> 00:59:23,711
Daddy.
It's me.

559
00:59:23,745 --> 00:59:26,314
Can you come early?

560
00:59:26,348 --> 00:59:33,254
Something's wrong...

561
00:59:33,288 --> 00:59:35,756
I think mommy's mad at me.

562
00:59:35,791 --> 00:59:38,292
Come home daddy, OK?

563
00:59:48,136 --> 00:59:50,137
- What are you doing?
- I got you, man.

564
00:59:50,172 --> 00:59:52,139
- I could have shot you.
- But you didn't.

565
00:59:52,174 --> 00:59:54,108
Let's get out of here.
There's nothing around here.

566
00:59:54,142 --> 00:59:55,843
No, there's something
around here.

567
00:59:55,878 --> 00:59:57,745
Like dead fish.

568
00:59:59,314 --> 01:00:01,282
Look familiar?

569
01:00:01,316 --> 01:00:04,352
Yeah...
It does.

570
01:00:20,903 --> 01:00:22,236
[scream]

571
01:00:30,579 --> 01:00:32,780
<i>Alex...</i>

572
01:00:34,650 --> 01:00:36,551
<i>Alex?</i>

573
01:00:42,191 --> 01:00:44,492
I don't wanna stay
with mommy.

574
01:00:44,526 --> 01:00:46,827
Can I go over to grandma's?

575
01:00:46,862 --> 01:00:49,864
Please.
I can take my bike.

576
01:00:53,101 --> 01:00:55,837
Daddy...

577
01:00:55,871 --> 01:00:58,439
Do you still love me?

578
01:01:01,543 --> 01:01:03,211
Bye, daddy.

579
01:01:12,020 --> 01:01:13,821
Yo!

580
01:01:44,453 --> 01:01:46,387
Perez, there's a kid.

581
01:01:46,421 --> 01:01:47,889
Ten-four.

582
01:02:09,912 --> 01:02:11,412
Police!
Don't move!

583
01:02:11,446 --> 01:02:13,447
I said don't move!

584
01:02:29,498 --> 01:02:30,831
Are you OK?

585
01:02:37,506 --> 01:02:40,842
I'm telling you man...

586
01:02:40,876 --> 01:02:43,211
followed me around
for two days.

587
01:02:43,245 --> 01:02:44,579
Two days...

588
01:02:44,613 --> 01:02:47,582
Just gettin' closer
and closer.

589
01:02:49,051 --> 01:02:50,852
So what'd you do?

590
01:02:57,192 --> 01:02:58,626
Help me!

591
01:02:58,660 --> 01:03:00,361
Please.
Help me!

592
01:03:00,395 --> 01:03:02,330
Hey.
What's wrong?

593
01:03:03,065 --> 01:03:04,398
She's out--

594
01:03:04,433 --> 01:03:05,533
Calm down.

595
01:03:05,567 --> 01:03:07,335
- Let him take the boy.
- She's out there!

596
01:03:07,369 --> 01:03:08,636
Nobody's out there.

597
01:03:08,670 --> 01:03:10,037
Just breathe.

598
01:03:10,072 --> 01:03:11,272
Breathe.

599
01:03:11,306 --> 01:03:13,140
Nobody's gonna hurt ya.

600
01:03:14,076 --> 01:03:15,243
No.
Please.

601
01:03:15,277 --> 01:03:16,944
Just tell me how
to get out of here.

602
01:03:16,979 --> 01:03:18,813
Just leave some for me.

603
01:03:26,021 --> 01:03:28,089
Come back here you bitch!

604
01:03:39,468 --> 01:03:41,802
What the hell...

605
01:03:45,507 --> 01:03:47,275
[screams]

606
01:03:56,418 --> 01:03:58,753
<i>Alex...</i>

607
01:04:02,824 --> 01:04:05,526
<i>I know you.</i>

608
01:04:35,424 --> 01:04:36,924
[boy screaming]

609
01:05:05,120 --> 01:05:06,487
Baby?

610
01:05:07,489 --> 01:05:09,690
<i>He's mine...</i>

611
01:05:29,411 --> 01:05:30,778
Perez.

612
01:05:33,549 --> 01:05:34,916
Perez.

613
01:05:36,451 --> 01:05:38,352
La Llorona.

614
01:05:39,655 --> 01:05:40,755
Just hold on.

615
01:05:40,789 --> 01:05:42,290
You're gonna be okay.

616
01:05:42,324 --> 01:05:45,393
I'm gonna get help...

617
01:05:45,427 --> 01:05:48,162
Just, stay there.
You're gonna be okay.

618
01:05:49,331 --> 01:05:51,265
Ten-thirteen.
Officer down.

619
01:05:51,300 --> 01:05:53,801
Underneath the...fuck!

620
01:05:53,836 --> 01:05:56,103
Underneath the tunnel,
underneath East Park Drive.

621
01:05:56,138 --> 01:05:57,872
Need assistance!

622
01:05:59,374 --> 01:06:01,108
Perez.

623
01:06:03,045 --> 01:06:05,313
Perez.

624
01:06:09,818 --> 01:06:11,085
Please!

625
01:06:11,119 --> 01:06:13,254
Anyone!
Help!

626
01:06:13,288 --> 01:06:16,524
Anyone!
I have my son!

627
01:06:16,558 --> 01:06:18,059
Help!

628
01:07:08,544 --> 01:07:10,878
Police!
Put the kid down!

629
01:07:11,780 --> 01:07:14,215
Stop!
And put the kid down!

630
01:07:14,249 --> 01:07:15,449
Help.

631
01:07:15,484 --> 01:07:18,920
I can't help you
until you put the kid down!

632
01:07:23,926 --> 01:07:25,560
Get your hands
off the kid!

633
01:07:25,594 --> 01:07:27,094
No, she's here!

634
01:07:27,129 --> 01:07:31,799
Let...him...go!

635
01:07:31,834 --> 01:07:33,000
Help us.

636
01:07:33,035 --> 01:07:35,603
It's okay, mama.
Let me go.

637
01:07:43,545 --> 01:07:44,912
Don't move!

638
01:07:44,947 --> 01:07:46,581
I have to hold him.

639
01:07:46,615 --> 01:07:49,717
She can't hurt you
if you're not afraid.

640
01:07:51,053 --> 01:07:53,821
Lady!
I said don't move!

641
01:07:53,856 --> 01:07:55,790
You have to help him.
She's here.

642
01:07:55,824 --> 01:07:56,991
Who's here?

643
01:07:57,025 --> 01:07:58,593
She wants him - my baby.

644
01:07:58,627 --> 01:08:00,328
What are you talking about?

645
01:08:00,362 --> 01:08:03,064
She's real.
You know she's real.

646
01:08:03,098 --> 01:08:05,066
He's mine.

647
01:08:05,100 --> 01:08:07,235
- Who are you?
- I have to hold him.

648
01:08:08,070 --> 01:08:10,738
Stop!
I said stop!!

649
01:08:12,074 --> 01:08:13,441
Tonio?

650
01:08:13,475 --> 01:08:14,809
Where is he!

651
01:08:14,843 --> 01:08:16,611
Tonio!

652
01:08:42,838 --> 01:08:44,372
<i>Daddy...</i>

653
01:08:44,606 --> 01:08:46,807
Where is he?

654
01:08:46,842 --> 01:08:48,209
Tell me!

655
01:08:48,243 --> 01:08:50,478
<i>You're like me...Cursed.</i>

656
01:08:50,512 --> 01:08:52,380
Tell me!

657
01:08:55,684 --> 01:08:57,685
Don't listen.

658
01:08:59,054 --> 01:09:00,888
Don't listen.

659
01:09:02,457 --> 01:09:04,258
