662
01:10:13,161 --> 01:10:14,829
[man screaming]

663
01:10:20,969 --> 01:10:23,638
Tonio!

664
01:10:52,835 --> 01:10:57,905
<i>Maria...</i>

665
01:10:57,940 --> 01:11:02,243
<i>Cry with me.</i>

666
01:12:01,737 --> 01:12:03,171
Stop!

667
01:12:29,631 --> 01:12:31,265
No! No!

668
01:12:32,201 --> 01:12:34,168
[child screaming]

669
01:13:00,929 --> 01:13:02,697
[Maria screaming]

670
